wiki.content:
"Just Don't Give a Fuck" (known as "Just Don't Give" in the clean version of The Slim Shady LP) is a song by American rapper Eminem and is the first single from The Slim Shady EP. The original version of this track was on Eminem's independent demo release The Slim Shady EP. The song did not do well as a single in the charts but was included on Eminem's second studio album The Slim Shady LP with a different instrumental, once he signed to Dr. Dre's Aftermath Entertainment.
